      • onReceiveCommand

        public abstract java.lang.String onReceiveCommand(java.lang.String command)
        Abstract method that performs the transaction

        When in contact with a device having the reader app, it will send a command that will call this function.

        You need to override this function, parse the received command and send back a suitable message/data as per the needs of your applicaiton

        Specified by:
        onReceiveCommand in class CardEmulationWrapperService
        Parameters:
        command - - Command received from the Card Reader device
        Returns:
        - The message that needs to be sent back to the reader.
